<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Réinitialisation de mot de passe</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #C0A57D;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Bonjour,</h1>

        <p>Pour réinitialiser votre mot de passe, cliquez sur le lien ci-dessous.</p>

        {% set reset_url = absolute_url(url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token})) %}
        {% if 'localhost' in reset_url and ':8000' not in reset_url %}
            {% set reset_url = reset_url|replace({'http://localhost': 'http://localhost:8000'}) %}
        {% endif %}
        <a href="{{ reset_url }}">
            Réinitialiser mon mot de passe
        </a>

        <p class="footer">Ce lien expire dans 1 heure.</p>

        <p class="footer">CinéCourts</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>